metadata.name: Views
metadata.description:
The sun offers significance to many poignant memories in our lives. Forever gracing us with its warmth, consistently rejuvenating us with its energetic powers. To a cat, the sun is a daily greeting, smiling from beyond a window. In music, the sun is a word sung about to represent warm days and joy. To a cup of tea, the sun is a perfect pairing to surmise the possibilities of a new day. What does the sun mean to you?

To learn more about Creatrix, the artist of this airdrop, visit http://www.annxliu.com/ & follow @annxliu on Twitter & Instagram
